SIZE=(14,67), ORIENT=(02,07)
WINDOW BOX
EASEL ON


                  Customer Relationship Code - Help

    Limits the accounts in a relationship based on the valid
    RCIF relationship code of the account defined on MICM Record
    7104 (Customer Relationship Codes).  If the Primary
    Relationship Codes option is used, the primary account's
    relationship will not be validated in this table.  If the
    Customer Relationship Code field is left blank, this option
    is not used.
